Summary:

Roundabout is a mergebot which integrates Github and Hudson to test and disposition pull requests from Github forks.

Here is a simplified diagram of the workflow: http://popplet.com/app/#/11752



Required packages:

GitPython==0.3.1
PyYAML==3.09
gitdb==0.5.2
github2>=0.2.0
lxml==2.3beta1

And if you want to run the tests/pylint/pep8:
nose==0.11.4
pep8==0.6.1
pylint==0.22.0
